# model: ARMA(0,1)-EGARCH(1,1)
# r_t = _t + a_t
# _t = _0 - _1 * a_t-1
# a_t = _t * _t
# ln[(_t)^2] = _0 + [_1*(_t-1) + _1(|_t-1| - E|_t-1|)] + _1*ln[(_t-1)^2]
# where _0 = 0, _1 = -0.96347, _0 = -0.98647, _1 = 0, _1 = 0.89404, _1 = 0.44817
# skew > 0, ; shape > 3, 
# _1 = 0,
